No. 08-1315. Pharmacia Corporation, et al., Petitioners v. Alaska Electrical Pension Fund, et al. 559 U.S. 1116, 130 S. Ct. 2401,

176 L. Ed. 2d 941,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 3687. May 3, 2010.

Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 554 F.3d 342.
